Microservice Performance Monitoring
│
├─ 1. Objectives
│   ├─ Detect latency & bottlenecks
│   ├─ Track throughput & load
│   ├─ Identify errors & failures
│   └─ Optimize resource utilization
│
├─ 2. Metrics
│   ├─ Application Metrics
│   │   ├─ Request Latency
│   │   ├─ Error Rate / Exceptions
│   │   ├─ Throughput (RPS)
│   │   └─ Service-specific metrics (business KPIs)
│   ├─ System Metrics
│   │   ├─ CPU / Memory Usage
│   │   ├─ Disk I/O
│   │   └─ Network throughput
│   └─ Custom Metrics
│       └─ Domain-specific metrics via instrumentation
│
├─ 3. Logging
│   ├─ Centralized Logging
│   │   ├─ ELK Stack (Elasticsearch, Logstash, Kibana)
│   │   ├─ Fluentd / Fluent Bit
│   │   └─ Loki / Grafana
│   └─ Structured & Contextual Logs
│       ├─ Correlate with trace IDs
│       └─ Include request context and metadata
│
├─ 4. Distributed Tracing
│   ├─ Purpose
│   │   ├─ Track requests across services
│   │   ├─ Identify latency bottlenecks
│   │   └─ Map service dependencies
│   ├─ Tools
│   │   ├─ OpenTelemetry
│   │   ├─ Jaeger
│   │   ├─ Zipkin
│   │   ├─ LightStep
│   │   └─ Grafana Tempo
│   └─ Data Collected
│       ├─ Trace IDs & Span IDs
│       ├─ Request timings
│       └─ Annotations / metadata
│
├─ 5. Alerts & Notifications
│   ├─ Threshold-based Alerts
│   ├─ Anomaly Detection / AI Ops
│   └─ Integration
│       ├─ PagerDuty
│       ├─ OpsGenie
│       └─ Slack / Email
│
├─ 6. Visualization & Dashboards
│   ├─ Grafana
│   ├─ Kibana
│   ├─ Datadog Dashboards
│   └─ New Relic / Dynatrace
│
├─ 7. Monitoring Tools
│   ├─ Prometheus
│   │   └─ Metrics scraping & alerting
│   ├─ Grafana
│   │   └─ Visualization
│   ├─ Datadog / New Relic / Dynatrace
│   │   └─ Full-stack observability + APM
│   ├─ OpenTelemetry
│   │   └─ Instrumentation + traces + metrics
│   └─ ELK / Loki
│       └─ Centralized logging
│
├─ 8. Best Practices
│   ├─ Instrument all services & critical paths
│   ├─ Correlate logs, metrics, and traces
│   ├─ Monitor both application & infrastructure
│   ├─ Use SLIs, SLOs, SLAs
│   ├─ Automate alerts & remediation
│   └─ Continuously analyze and optimize performance
